25-Line Coliseum Poker is played with 25 decks, each consisting of 52 cards. It differs from the original Coliseum Poker, since it has several lines of cards. Each line makes use of a different deck and is treated as a separate hand. When several hands are won, your winnings are summed up. The game includes the Progressive Jackpot option! To win a Jackpot you need to place the maximum bet of 5 coins and get Royal Flush combination.  1.3% of each bet placed in the game is added to a common pot.